## Tool Access Control

### Toolset Groups

Toolsets group related tools for easier management via `TOOLSETS` env var or `--toolsets` flag.

**Jira Toolsets ({{ counts.jira_toolsets }}):**

| Toolset | Core | Tools |
|---------|:----:|-------|
